{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And going through Cologne, a cousin of my father's, you know-- I don't know how she found me, among all this, this train passing through, all those children on it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But suddenly there she was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had come to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she didn't make it out, and neither-- they went to France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And their whole family perished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I recall her being there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was sort of a, a last farewell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I recall getting on the ferry in Holland and being seasick on the, on the Channel, and-- I really-- it's, it's really peculiar how my recollections of the Kristallnacht are absolutely clear.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, you know, I haven't forgotten a thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Whereas, of this actual leaving, it's kind of hazy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember being picked up in, in London by these ladies, who, you know, said, are you tired?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, what on earth is, are you tired?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, what language have I been studying?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it, it turned out she-- what she was saying is, are you tired.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were very kind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, they got us to the schools, and-- yes?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do, do you know how you were chosen to be part of the transport?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, there were friends of friends of my parents, who lived in England, who had somehow settled in England and had managed to get this family to come to England and, and also their children to, to come to England-- and, and, and-- because they knew this Mrs.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pickard, who had, who had organized this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have-- again, when I was in Germany a couple of years ago, I met a nephew of theirs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I still don't quite know just how this, how this all was organized.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
